'''三氟乙酸汞'''是一种汞化合物，化学式为Hg(CF<sub>3</sub>COO)<sub>2</sub>。它可由[[氧化汞|氧化汞]]和[[三氟乙酸|三氟乙酸]]反应制得。<ref name=RA>{{cite journal|journal=Canadian Journal of Chemistry|volume=35|issue=12|language=en|issn=0008-4042|date=1957-12-01|pages=1377–1383|doi=10.1139/v57-182|url=http://www.nrcresearchpress.com/doi/10.1139/v57-182|title=REVERSIBILITY OF ALKENE OXYMERCURATION|accessdate=2021-01-09|author=A. Rodgman, D. A. Shearer, George F Wright}}</ref>它可以和[[吡啶|吡啶]]形成配合物Hg(C<sub>5</sub>H<sub>5</sub>N)<sub>3</sub>(CF<sub>3</sub>COO)<sub>2</sub>。<ref>{{cite journal|journal=Acta Crystallographica Section B Structural Crystallography and Crystal Chemistry|volume=34|issue=12|issn=0567-7408|date=1978-12-01|pages=3758–3760|doi=10.1107/S0567740878012108|url=http://scripts.iucr.org/cgi-bin/paper?S0567740878012108|title=Structure of tris(pyridine)mercury(II) bis(trifluoroacetate)|accessdate=2021-01-09|author=J. Halfpenny, R. W. H. Small|archive-date=2018-06-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180603084907/http://scripts.iucr.org/cgi-bin/paper?S0567740878012108}}</ref>在KF的存在下，它和(CF<sub>3</sub>)<sub>2</sub>C=CF<sub>2</sub>在DMF中反应，可以得到[(CF<sub>3</sub>)<sub>3</sub>C]<sub>2</sub>Hg。<ref>Martynov, B. I.; Sterlin, S. R.; Dyatkin, B. L. Reactions of perfluorocarbanions with mercury trifluoroacetate and trifluoromethyltrifluoroacetate. ''Izvestiya Akademii Nauk SSSR, Seriya Khimicheskaya'', 1974. 7: 1642-1643. ISSN: 0002-3353.</ref>

它可用于有机合成，其反应活性和[[乙酸汞|乙酸汞]]相似，但亲电性更强。<ref name=Pub2 />

